{"title":"绿，融在生活里","authors":["董宇峰"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿，融在生活里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董宇峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！厂区——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一寸土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都植满翠绿的草皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场有花坛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楼前有树林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路旁有小溪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂，再不是灰色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空气里贮满了绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖水里荡漾着绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同高大的厂房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸润着浓浓的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓浓的绿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿，生命的绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们走来。我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向生命的绿色走去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿，是生命本来的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们却有过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻易的丢失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和如饥似渴的寻觅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在失去绿色的日子里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"污染和灰暗就包围了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的生活啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，绿色的队伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始在大地蔓延，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树木、鲜花、小草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严地守卫着厂区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才有了爽目的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才有了清新的空气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿，崭新的绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融在生活里。我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱绿，赞美绿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一块草皮是一面旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一朵鲜花是一把火炬……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}